snippet.title: Paradroid 90 (Amiga) | No commentary, 720p 50FPS
snippet.description:
💾 More Amiga games ► https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLEXiKm54CARSqoV4Bhhge9ubCRqxCO8Pm
📙 The Amiga version of the 1985 Commodore 64 game by Andrew Braybrook. A unique game where you control a device capable of attaching itself to robots and assuming control by hacking their brains.
